title: Two men mushroom picking find large footprint and snapped tree near Elkton
observed: While collecting mushrooms i came across a huge footprint. The area was thick with brush', and knowing i didn't believe i saw what i saw.   my hair still stands with the thought ...my friend and i will never forget. the print was indented and around 18 inches long and 8 inches wide
location_details: off hwy 138 w half mile south of elkton turnwest across umpqua river proceed a mile turn right on camp cr road up in the hills
